rComments: I don't think I've ever encountered such an enthusiastic professor in all my years. She really cares about every student she has and isn't afraid to really engage with you if you so desire. She really wants everyone in the class to know each other as well, which was really nice after the initial awkwardness. Not an easy grade, but would recommend!
